des:
The former president has been a ratings magnet for years. Hear the top headlines from the conservative right and the liberal left. 

Here’s a sample from the past.

“There are two kinds of people, those that believe all men are created equal, and Republicans.”

And here’s another gem from the archives.

"George Washington couldn’t tell a lie and Richard Nixon couldn’t tell the truth. Donald Trump couldn’t tell the difference.”

Get the latest headlines. We strive to stay current.
